Llama Lords is a gaming clan, we play CSS, WoW, TF2 and more.
Please play on our Gun Game server

This map is an abstract design - when first playing on this map think like Spiderman. Lord Azael came up with the idea for this map and provided Karnage with designs. The idea was inspired by gg_project_funkeh (made by [LL] Sibby) which has extraordinarily large ladders. The idea came about during a knife fight on said ladders. Many thanks to Llama Lords for ideas/support/testing


Please visit the clan website www.llamalords.co.uk
This map can be uploaded to other download portals if needs be.
Ask my permission before editing or decompiling the map.
Steam: explosivose
